{"tid":1944793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★友邦有財務策劃顧問初步確診","createTime":"2020-03-26T15:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T17:00:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba332ed27ed1bb80c7a11fa7f0690032cca3c43d","tid":1944793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"友邦香港發言人表示，確認一名財務策劃顧問初步確診感染新型冠狀病毒，目前正留院接受治療。該名被確診的財務策劃顧問在銅鑼灣利園2期的辦公室工作，最後一次回辦公室為3月18日並全程均有戴上口罩，過去14日均沒有外遊記錄，亦没有接觸任何客戶。<br />\n<br />\n該名財務策劃顧問於3月13日曾與一名於3月21日確診患者共同用饍。友邦將為該財務策劃顧問及其家人提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200326/bkn-20200326170809159-0326_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200326%2Fbkn-20200326170809159-0326_00842_001.html&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR8v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=8af047a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200326/bkn-20200326170809159-0326_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a12ea344e5172c0d4355f46966a775bc269e63b3","tid":1944793,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"財務策劃顧問其實係咪姐係成日叫你借錢個d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f818dc8c11bff1b06a9d5f445b9dd98de0a5855f","tid":1944793,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12ea344e5172c0d4355f46966a775bc269e63b3","tid":1944793,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"財務策劃顧問其實係咪姐係成日叫你借錢個d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"成日叫支那人落黎睇醫生買保險果啲"},{"pid":"77875977a3fbf4eb111eb3edcdf4384a70c78170","tid":1944793,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12ea344e5172c0d4355f46966a775bc269e63b3","